mediator - package mediator
 
model - package model
 
Model - Interface in model
Interface extending interfaces ModelEmployee, ModelUser, UnnamedPropertyChangeSubject.
ModelDatabase - Class in model
Class implementing ModelPersistence interface, ensuring persistence of the system by creating sql statements and running them in relational database (written in postgres)
ModelDatabase(Model) - Constructor for class model.ModelDatabase
1 argument constructor, setting model instance variable and setting up connection with database using class MyDatabaseV2
ModelEmployee - Interface in model
Interface containing methods related functionalities to of the system created for the shop's employees
ModelManager - Class in model
Class implementing Model interface, connecting all classes in the Model package, executing all important actions related to the system, "brain" of the whole application
ModelManager() - Constructor for class model.ModelManager
O argument constructor, loading information from database into instance variables that will be used while displaying data to client, establishing this class as subject in observer pattern
ModelPersistence - Interface in model
Interface containing methods related to persistence of the system (in this version, persistence is achieved with use of database)
ModelUser - Interface in model
Interface containing methods related functionalities to of the system created for the shop's customers
MyDatabasev2 - Class in model
Class responsible for actual connection with database, except one method which is changed and that will be documented here.
